427
00:38:15.575 --> 00:38:18.911
- Det var så...
- Det var virkelig...


428
00:38:18.995 --> 00:38:20.497
Ja.

429
00:38:23.249 --> 00:38:25.835
Gad vide, hvor det fly skal hen.

